# Topic 2: GeometricField Deep Dive - The Complete CFD Object

## **GeometricField Architecture: The Foundation of OpenFOAM CFD**

### **Class Hierarchy and Template Structure**

[Diagram: โครงสร้างของ GeometricField template inheritance]

```cpp
// GeometricField template definition:
template<class Type, class PatchField, class GeoMesh>
class GeometricField : public DimensionedField<Type, GeoMesh>
{
    // Type: scalar, vector, tensor, etc.
    // PatchField: boundary field type
    // GeoMesh: mesh topology type
};

// Common specializations:
typedef GeometricField<scalar, fvPatchField, volMesh>    volScalarField;
typedef GeometricField<vector, fvPatchField, volMesh>    volVectorField;
typedef GeometricField<tensor, fvPatchField, volMesh>    volTensorField;
typedef GeometricField<scalar, fvsPatchField, surfaceMesh> surfaceScalarField;
```

**พารามิเตอร์ Template:**
- **Type parameter**: กำหนดประเภทของวัตถุทางคณิตศาสตร์ (scalar, vector, tensor)
- **PatchField parameter**: ระบุวิธีการจัดการ boundary conditions
- **GeoMesh parameter**: กำหนด spatial discretization topology

### **Data Structure and Memory Layout**

```cpp
// Internal structure:
class GeometricField
{
private:
    // Core data storage
    Field<Type> field_;                    // Cell/face/point values
    PtrList<PatchField<Type>> boundaryField_;  // Boundary conditions
    
    // Reference to computational mesh
    const GeoMesh& mesh_;
    
    // Time and I/O information
    const word& name_;
    const Time& time_;
    
public:
    // Access methods
    const Field<Type>& internalField() const { return field_; }
    Field<Type>& internalField() { return field_; }
    
    const PatchField<Type>& boundaryField()[label patchi] const 
    { 
        return boundaryField_[patchi]; 
    }
    
    // Geometric operations
    tmp<GeometricField<typename innerProduct<Type, Type>::type, 
                       PatchField, GeoMesh>> 
    dot(const GeometricField<Type, PatchField, GeoMesh>&) const;
};
```

**การออกแบบหน่วยความจำ:**
- **Field Storage**: ใช้ contiguous memory allocation เพื่อ cache performance ที่ดีที่สุด
- **Boundary Field Management**: เก็บ boundary conditions ใน PtrList เพื่อรองรับประเภทที่แตกต่างกัน
- **Mesh Reference**: รักษาการอ้างอิงไปยัง computational mesh สำหรับ spatial discretization
- **Time Coupling**: ผสานรวมกับระบบจัดการเวลาของ OpenFOAM

### **Construction and Initialization Patterns**

| Pattern | การใช้งาน | คุณสมบัติหลัก |
|---------|-------------|--------------|
| **File-based** | อ่านจากไฟล์ | `IOobject::MUST_READ`, `IOobject::AUTO_WRITE` |
| **Programmatic** | สร้างด้วยโปรแกรม | `IOobject::NO_READ`, กำหนดค่าเริ่มต้น |
| **Copy with modification** | คัดลอกและแก้ไข | `IOobject::NO_WRITE`, ใช้ mathematical operations |

```cpp
// Pattern 1: File-based construction
volScalarField T
(
    IOobject
    (
        "T",                    // Field name
        runTime.timeName(),     // Time directory
        mesh,                   // Mesh reference
        IOobject::MUST_READ,    // Must read from file
        IOobject::AUTO_WRITE    // Auto-write during simulation
    ),
    mesh
);

// Pattern 2: Programmatic construction
volVectorField U
(
    IOobject
    (
        "U",                    // Field name
        runTime.timeName(),     // Time directory  
        mesh,                   // Mesh reference
        IOobject::NO_READ,      // Don't read from file
        IOobject::AUTO_WRITE    // Auto-write during simulation
    ),
    mesh,
    dimensionedVector("zero", dimensionSet(0,1,-1,0,0,0), vector::zero)  // Initial value
);

// Pattern 3: Copy construction with modification
volScalarField pModified
(
    IOobject
    (
        "pModified",            // New field name
        runTime.timeName(),     // Time directory
        mesh,                   // Mesh reference
        IOobject::NO_READ,      // Don't read from file
        IOobject::NO_WRITE      // Don't write automatically
    ),
    p * 1.5 + 1e5              // Mathematical operation on existing field
);
```

### **Spatial Operations and Differential Operators**

**Finite Volume Calculus Operations:**

```cpp
// Finite Volume Calculus Operations:
namespace fvc  // Finite Volume Calculus
{
    // First-order derivatives
    template<class Type>
    tmp<GeometricField<typename outerProduct<vector, Type>::type, 
                       fvPatchField, volMesh>>
    grad(const GeometricField<Type, fvPatchField, volMesh>&);

    template<class Type>
    tmp<GeometricField<Type, fvPatchField, volMesh>>
    div(const GeometricField<Type, fvsPatchField, surfaceMesh>&);

    template<class Type>
    tmp<GeometricField<Type, fvPatchField, volMesh>>
    laplacian(const GeometricField<Type, fvPatchField, volMesh>&);

    // Interpolation operators
    template<class Type>
    tmp<GeometricField<Type, fvsPatchField, surfaceMesh>>
    interpolate(const GeometricField<Type, fvPatchField, volMesh>&);

    // Time derivatives
    template<class Type>
    tmp<GeometricField<Type, fvPatchField, volMesh>>
    ddt(const GeometricField<Type, fvPatchField, volMesh>&);
}

// Usage in CFD equations:
volVectorField U = ...;  // Velocity field
volScalarField p = ...;  // Pressure field

// Momentum equation terms:
auto convectiveTerm = fvc::div(U * U);           // ∇·(U⊗U)
auto pressureGrad = fvc::grad(p);               // ∇p
auto viscousTerm = fvc::laplacian(nu, U);       // ∇·(ν∇U)
auto timeDerivative = fvc::ddt(U);              // ∂U/∂t
```

[Diagram: การทำงานของ spatial operations บาน mesh topology]

### **Boundary Condition Integration**

```cpp
// Boundary condition handling architecture:
template<class Type>
class fvPatchField : public Field<Type>
{
protected:
    const fvPatch& patch_;      // Reference to boundary patch
    const DimensionedField<Type, volMesh>& internalField_;
    
public:
    // Virtual interface for different boundary types
    virtual void updateCoeffs() = 0;
    virtual tmp<Field<Type>> gradientInternalCoeffs() const = 0;
    virtual tmp<Field<Type>> valueInternalCoeffs() const = 0;
    
    // Matrix coefficient contributions
    virtual void addBoundaryDiag(scalarField&, const direction) const = 0;
    virtual void addBoundarySource(scalarField&) const = 0;
};

// Example boundary condition implementations:
class fixedValueFvPatchField : public fvPatchField<Type>
{
    // Dirichlet boundary: fixed value at boundary
    virtual void updateCoeffs() override { /* set specified values */ }
};

class fixedGradientFvPatchField : public fvPatchField<Type> 
{
    // Neumann boundary: fixed gradient at boundary
    virtual void updateCoeffs() override { /* maintain gradient */ }
};

class wallFunctionFvPatchField : public fvPatchField<Type>
{
    // Wall function boundary: complex wall treatment
    virtual void updateCoeffs() override { /* compute wall values */ }
};
```

### **Parallel Computing Integration**

```cpp
// Parallel data management in GeometricField:
template<class Type>
class GeometricField
{
    // Automatic parallel decomposition handling
    void distribute(const labelList& distributionMaping)
    {
        // 1. Send field data to appropriate processors
        // 2. Update boundary conditions between subdomains
        // 3. Handle processor-to-processor communication
    }
    
    // Synchronization for coupled boundaries
    void correctBoundaryConditions()
    {
        // Ensure consistency at processor boundaries
        forAll(boundaryField_, patchi)
        {
            if (boundaryField_[patchi].coupled())
            {
                boundaryField_[patchi].initEvaluate();  // Start communication
                boundaryField_[patchi].evaluate();      // Complete communication
            }
        }
    }
};

// Automatic MPI communication for coupled patches:
class processorFvPatchField : public fvPatchField<Type>
{
    virtual void evaluate() override
    {
        // 1. Send boundary data to neighboring processor
        // 2. Receive boundary data from neighboring processor  
        // 3. Apply coupling conditions (averaging, interpolation)
    }
};
```

**Algorithm: Parallel Synchronization Process**

1. **Initiate Communication**: ส่งข้อมูลไปยัง processors ข้างเคียง
2. **Exchange Data**: รับข้อมูลจาก processors ข้างเคียง
3. **Apply Coupling Conditions**: ใช้เงื่อนไขการ coupling (averaging, interpolation)
4. **Update Field Values**: อัปเดตค่า field ที่ processor boundaries

### **Performance Optimization Features**

```cpp
// Temporary field management for expression templates:
template<class Type>
class tmp
{
private:
    Type* ptr_;
    bool ref_;
    
public:
    // Automatic memory management
    ~tmp() { if (!ref_ && ptr_) delete ptr_; }
    
    // Move semantics for efficient passing
    tmp(const tmp& t) : ptr_(t.ptr_), ref_(t.ref_) 
    { 
        t.ptr_ = nullptr;  // Transfer ownership
    }
    
    // Automatic reference counting
    Type& operator*() { return *ptr_; }
    const Type& operator*() const { return *ptr_; }
};

// Usage with expression templates:
auto result = fvc::grad(p) + 2.0 * fvc::laplacian(T);
// 1. No temporary field allocations for intermediate results
// 2. Single allocation for final result
// 3. Automatic cleanup when tmp goes out of scope
```

**ประโยชน์ด้านประสิทธิภาพ:**
- **Expression Templates**: ลดการจองหน่วยความจำสำหรับผลลัพธ์ระดับกลาง
- **Move Semantics**: การถ่ายโอนความเป็นเจ้าของที่มีประสิทธิภาพ
- **Automatic Cleanup**: การจัดการหน่วยความจำโดยอัตโนมัติ

### **Advanced Features and Specializations**

**Table: GeometricField Specializations**

| Specialization | การใช้งาน | Mesh Type | ตัวอย่างการใช้งาน |
|----------------|-------------|-----------|-------------------|
| `volScalarField` | Cell-centered scalar values | Volume mesh | Temperature, pressure |
| `volVectorField` | Cell-centered vector values | Volume mesh | Velocity |
| `surfaceScalarField` | Face-centered scalar values | Surface mesh | Flux calculations |
| `pointVectorField` | Point-centered vector values | Point mesh | Mesh motion |

```cpp
// Field mapping between different mesh types:
template<class Type, class GeoMesh>
void GeometricField<Type, PatchField, GeoMesh>::map
(
    const GeometricField<Type, PatchField, GeoMesh>& fieldToMap,
    const meshToMesh& mapper
)
{
    // Interpolate field from one mesh to another
    // Handles mesh refinement/coarsening, geometry changes
}

// Point field specialization for mesh motion:
typedef GeometricField<vector, pointPatchField, pointMesh> pointVectorField;

// Surface field specialization for flux calculations:  
typedef GeometricField<scalar, fvsPatchField, surfaceMesh> surfaceScalarField;

// Complex field support for acoustics, electromagnetics:
typedef GeometricField<complexScalar, fvPatchField, volMesh> volComplexScalarField;
```

## **สรุป GeometricField**

The GeometricField class represents OpenFOAM's answer to the fundamental challenge of CFD software design: how to represent physical fields that simultaneously have mathematical, physical, and computational properties.

**ข้อดีหลัก:**
- **Integration**: รวม dimensional analysis, spatial discretization, boundary conditions, และ parallel computing
- **Abstraction**: เขียน CFD code ที่อ่านง่ายเหมือนกับ governing equations
- **Optimization**: จัดการรายละเอียดของ numerical discretization, memory management, และ parallel computation โดยอัตโนมัติ

**แนวทางการพัฒนา:**
1. Focus on physics rather than numerical implementation
2. Leverage automatic I/O and data management
3. Utilize built-in dimensional safety
4. Take advantage of mesh-aware operations
5. Exploit automatic parallelization capabilities
```
